{"timestamp": "2026-05-28 16:17:04,993", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.execution", "module": "flow", "function": "run_async", "line": 205, "message": " - task4: ```text\n1. Analyze the job description.\n2. Analyze the candidate resume.\n3. Candidate resume content missing. Unable to complete resume analysis.\n4. Generate tailored technical interview questions based on the job requirements.\n5. Send scheduling email to the candidate:\n\nSubject: Interview Invitation - [Job Title] at [Company Name]\n\nEmail Body:\n\nDear [Candidate Name],\n\nWe are pleased to invite you to interview for the [Job Title] position at [Company Name].\n\nThe interview is scheduled for [Date] at [Time] [Timezone]. Please confirm your availability.\n\n[Optional: Include a brief introduction of the interviewers and the interview format.]\n\nYou can use this link to join the meeting: [Meeting Link]\n\nIf this time does not work for you, please let me know your availability for other slots.\n\nWe look forward to speaking with you.\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]\n[Your Title]\n[Company Name]\n\nTone Tag: Semi-Formal\nPersonalization Tokens Used: [Candidate Name], [Job Title], [Company Name], [Date], [Time], [Timezone], [Meeting Link]\n\n6. Conduct technical interview using the generated questions.\n7. Record candidate responses for each question.\n\n8. Send follow-up email to the candidate after the interview:\n\nSubject: Following Up - [Job Title] Interview at [Company Name]\n\nEmail Body:\n\nDear [Candidate Name],\n\nThank you for taking the time to interview with us for the [Job Title] position at [Company Name] on [Date]. We appreciate you sharing your experience and insights.\n\nThe team will be discussing your interview and we will be in touch within [Number] business days regarding the next steps.\n\nIn the meantime, if you have any questions, please do not hesitate to reach out.\n\nThank you again for your interest in [Company Name].\n\nSincerely,\n[Your Name]\n[Your Title]\n[Company Name]\n\nTone Tag: Semi-Formal\nPersonalization Tokens Used: [Candidate Name], [Job Title], [Company Name], [Date], [Number]\n\n9. Score candidate responses based on ideal answer indicators and follow-up probes provided for each question.\n10. Generate final evaluation report including overall score, strengths, weaknesses, and recommendation (hire/no hire).\n```\n"}
